data.description: Fantastic colonial in great condition in Tabernacle! Gorgeous high-end chefs kitchen, stainless steel appliances, convection cook top, double oven, wet bar and wine fridge opens up to great room with vaulted ceiling, and two skylights.Brick fireplace and sliding doors to rear deck   Over an acre wooded yard for the nature enthusiast. Upstairs find four spacious bedrooms and two full baths, Top all of this off with a two car garage, and you have a beautiful home ready for its new owners, Newer septic system installed December 2021. This sale is subject to sellers finding suitable housing.
